                <h2 data-uuid="9cfde22518504b7c9970a79417ffe7c3">The Progressive Amendments, 1909–1920</h2>
                <p data-uuid="27b5949e5e1844989bdbbee7cc662e9d">Four amendments to the Constitution were proposed and ratified during the administration of President Woodrow Wilson.</p>
            </article>
